The paper discusses the formalization of enterprise application integration (EAI) solutions, which is a topic that falls under software engineering (cs.SE). The use of timed db-net also suggests a connection to distributed computing (cs.DC) and databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the formalization of integration patterns involves the use of formal languages and semantics, which relates to programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the focus on optimization and verification suggests a connection to control systems (cs.SY).
